manifest.name: coc.nvim
manifest.description: LSP based intellisense engine for neovim & vim8.
manifest.readme: This package contains typings of coc.nvim only. Files were exported from https://github.com/neoclide/coc.nvim/blob/master/typings ## Installation npm install --save-dev coc.nvim ## Support coc.nvim If you like my work, consider supporting me on Patreon or PayPal: ## Credits [Visual Studio Code](https://github.com/microsoft/vscode), and [Microsoft](https://github.com/microsoft)
